      },
      "date": "2014-09-26 17:04:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nThis patch fails compiling in my testbed with:\n cc1: warnings being treated as errors\n /home/green/git/lustre-release/lustre/llite/lproc_llite.c:  In function ???ll_max_cached_mb_seq_write???:\n /home/green/git/lustre-release/lustre/llite/lproc_llite.c:452: error: comparison of distinct pointer types lacks a cast\n make[6]: *** [/home/green/git/lustre-release/lustre/llite/lproc_llite.o] Error 1\n make[5]: *** [/home/green/git/lustre-release/lustre/llite] Error 2",
